comment: The best one I've tasted from the sea.  Woody, spicy and smooth!!
Smooth with a nice burn. Very tasty.

Not to sharp of a bite to start and dissipates fast.  Strong tastes of Tofee, What I taste as orange peel, and finishes with a very strong Creme Brulee note!  I haven't met a Bourbon I dont like, and this one sits in high regard.  This is a lovely "Experimental" bourbon!
